    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "At the moment there is no event triggered by InstantSearch each time something is refined. A possible solution is to leverage [the routing system](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/instantsearch/js/?language=js#widget-param-routing) to detect changes. But keep in mind that it was not designed for that and might not completely solve your use case. The safer solution would be unfortunately to build a custom widget.",
