    "body": "@samouss \r\n\r\nI have a workaround for the menuSelect : \r\n\r\n```\r\nsearch.on('render', function(){\r\n// target.event here\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\nI could target the select event when rendering.\r\n\r\nBut it's not really clean...\r\n\r\nThanks, ",
